{"id":"api/core/model","title":"model","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/model\", \"name\": \"model\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/authoring/model/model.ts#L97-L102\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"model\">model<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/model#model\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label const\">const</label>\n    <label class=\"api-status-label dev-preview\" title=\"此 API 仅供开发者预览\">\n      <a href=\"guide/releases#developer-preview\">开发者预览</a>\n    </label>\n    \n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"adnn3pgei9ihwra7fzdftqol1\"><code><a href=\"api/core/model\" class=\"code-anchor\">model</a></code>声明了一个可写信号，该信号作为包含指令的输入/输出对暴露出来。输入名称可以从类成员或\n<code>alias</code>选项中获取。输出名称是通过获取输入名称并附加\n<code>Change</code>来生成的。</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/core/model#description\">查看更多...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n  const <a href=\"api/core/model\" class=\"code-anchor\">model</a>: <a href=\"api/core/ModelFunction\" class=\"code-anchor\">ModelFunction</a>;\n  </code-example>\n\n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/model#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"a9en6cpq5cdlcan7n8q6ffosy\">使用初始值初始化一个模型。如果未指定明确值，Angular 将使用\n<code>undefined</code>。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dkmbszhvj4ycy0ofkfz7gtyio\">对于不需要初始值的模型，考虑使用\n<code>model.required</code>。</p>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9q9dtndqe78480cjpq6qtur6b\">更多信息请参阅\n<a href=\"api/core/model#usage-notes\">使用说明...</a></p>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/model#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"91zxitm8p4h785yd3xvlt3f9u\">通过声明一个类字段并使用\n<code><a href=\"api/core/model\" class=\"code-anchor\">model</a>()</code>或\n<code>model.required()</code>函数对您的指令或组件中的模型进行初始化。</p>\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>({..})\nexport class MyDir {\n  firstName = <a href=\"api/core/model\" class=\"code-anchor\">model</a>&lt;string&gt;();            // string|undefined\n  lastName = model.required&lt;string&gt;();    // string\n  age = <a href=\"api/core/model\" class=\"code-anchor\">model</a>(0);                         // number\n}\n</code-example>\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/ModelFunction\n - api/forms/FormControlDirective\n - api/forms/FormControlName\n - api/forms/NgModel\n - guide/form-validation\n - guide/forms\n - guide/lazy-loading-ngmodules\n - guide/model-inputs\n - guide/testing-components-scenarios\n - guide/upgrade\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/Directive\n - api/core/ModelFunction\n - api/core/model#description\n - api/core/model#model\n - api/core/model#usage-notes\n - guide/releases#developer-preview\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/authoring/model/model.ts#L97-L102\n-->"}